OL,5, An ITV executive has defended the      
OL,6, network's duty of care to staff after  
OL,7, the furore over Phillip Schofield's    
OL,8, affair with a much younger colleague.  
OL,10,FThe This Morning host left ITV last    
OL,11,Fmonth after admitting he lied to bosses
OL,12,Fand workmates about the affair.        
OL,14,FThere have also been allegations of a  
OL,15,Fwider "toxic" culture at the programme.
OL,17,FMagnus Brooke, ITV's director of       
OL,18,Fstrategy, policy and regulation, told  
OL,19,FMPs bullying was "unacceptable" and    
OL,20,Fwould be "dealt with appropriately".   
